**Problem50 (Truth table)**

Purpose:: 3個input,所以卡諾圖會有8個判斷結果,且鄰近的input一次只能改一個,隨後就可以得到Y=x3bar and x2+x3 and x1.

Source:https://hdlbits.01xz.net/wiki/Truthtable1

Exercise:
module top_module( 
    input x3,
    input x2,
    input x1,  // three inputs
    output f   // one output
);
    assign f= ~(x3)&x2|x3&x1;
endmodule
